name: Happy Spooky Day
description: Do you feel eyes on you everytime you're you're out amidst a crowd. Does it make you feel anxious? Do you have a problem making eye contact and speaking your mind? I do too. That's the ghost in us, the real demon we have a battle with. Our mental health. Take care of yourself, remember, there is always a way forward. A pumpkin perhaps. | @ayushbanerjee
